WEBVTT

00:03:59.658 --> 00:04:03.928
kutusaidia kutatua hili tatizo
linaloumiza wao, rafiki na familia zao.

00:04:03.952 --> 00:04:07.018
Tuliongea na watu waliofikia kuuza gari
ili kulipa bili ya afya,

00:04:07.042 --> 00:04:08.339
na kufilisika

00:04:08.363 --> 00:04:10.636
kuacha matibabu kwa sababu ya gharama.

00:04:11.230 --> 00:04:13.890
Fikiria ungeweza kumudu
gharama za uchunguzi

00:04:13.914 --> 00:04:15.430
lakini siyo matibabu.

00:04:17.589 --> 00:04:19.751
Tulianzisha majadiliano makubwa
juu ya gharama

00:04:19.775 --> 00:04:23.526
tukihusisha madaktari, mahospitali, ndiyo,
na wagonjwa wao,

00:04:23.550 --> 00:04:25.741
au tunavyopenda kuwaita, watu.

00:04:25.765 --> 00:04:27.669
(Kicheko)

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.670
Tulibadili sera.